      <body>
         <opener><dateline><date when="1916-02-07">February 7, 1916.</date></dateline>
            <salute>Dear <persName key="john_fletcher">J.G.F.</persName>:</salute></opener>
         <p>Here is the “Impressionist Picture of a Garden” which I promised you for the “Trimmed Lamp.” 
            I forgot to send it with the other things.</p> 
         <p>I am telephoning this from <placeName>town</placeName>, so I cannot sign it. </p>
         <closer>Affectionately yours,</closer>
      </body>
